<title>金价大涨</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E9%87%91%E4%BB%B7%E5%A4%A7%E6%B6%A8</link>
